    "It may be desirable to compensate for known uncertainties, such as intra-rater or inter-rater variability, by configuring the metric accordingly.",
    "This is only possible for some metrics.",
    "Structures of the provided class are only a few pixels in size.",
    "Example: multiple sclerosis lesions in MRI scans.",
